    "monster3322": "<h1 class=monster>Finch Household Guard<br><span class=type>Medium natural humanoid human , human</span><br><span class=level>Level 8 Minion Soldier<span class=xp> XP 88</span></span> </h1> <p class=flavor><b>Initiative</b> +6        <b>Senses</b> Perception +6<br><b>HP</b> 1; a missed attack never damages a minion.<br><b>AC</b> 22; <b>Fortitude</b> 20, <b>Reflex</b> 18, <b>Will</b> 18<br><b>Speed</b> 5</p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Longsword</b> (standard, at-will) </p><p class=flavorIndent>+13 vs AC; 6 damage. </p><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Weight of Numbers</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>If two or more Finch household guards hit the same target in the same round, the second attack also slows the target until the end of the second attacker's next turn.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Alignment</b> Chaotic evil       <b> Languages</b> Common<br><b>Str</b> 20 (+9)      <b>Dex</b> 15 (+6)      <b>Wis</b> 14 (+6)<br><b>Con</b> 16 (+7)      <b>Int</b> 11 (+4)      <b>Cha</b> 11 (+4)</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Equipment</b>: chainmail , longsword .</p><br><p class=publishedIn>Published in Eberron Campaign Setting, page(s) 255.</p>",
